208
00:15:53,580 --> 00:15:55,580
[SPEAKER_00] To je danas na snagi.

209
00:15:55,580 --> 00:16:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, mi više ne smijemo izgovarati istine

210
00:16:00,559 --> 00:16:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] jer to kao vrijeđa koga?

211
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:07,360
[SPEAKER_00] Imbicile? Idiote?

212
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:11,460
