219
00:16:30,740 --> 00:16:32,620
[SPEAKER_00] da živimo srednji vijek

220
00:16:32,620 --> 00:16:35,340
[SPEAKER_00] treba objašnjavati

221
00:16:35,340 --> 00:16:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] da je jednako

222
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:40,399
[SPEAKER_00] ako ja, evo, mog framaša, bivšeg iz Posušija

223
00:16:40,399 --> 00:16:43,100
