225
00:16:45,779 --> 00:16:51,620
[SPEAKER_00] Pazite, to je to što je rekao Dostojenstvi.

226
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je taj idiotizam.

227
00:16:53,940 --> 00:16:58,700
