232
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] Dok mi ne rješimo ta temeljna pitanja

233
00:17:15,900 --> 00:17:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, sve će se govoriti

234
00:17:17,599 --> 00:17:18,619
[SPEAKER_00] njih sve vrijedja.

235
00:17:18,619 --> 00:17:20,500
