238
00:17:29,579 --> 00:17:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] U svu tu priču

239
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:33,980
[SPEAKER_00] uplela se

240
00:17:33,980 --> 00:17:35,940
[SPEAKER_00] demokracija.

241
00:17:35,940 --> 00:17:40,519
[SPEAKER_00] Demokracija vam je,

242
00:17:40,519 --> 00:17:42,539
