243
00:17:42,539 --> 00:17:46,940
[SPEAKER_00] najmanje loš oblik vladanja.

244
00:17:46,940 --> 00:17:48,180
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ne kazaš istad,

245
00:17:48,180 --> 00:17:48,779
[SPEAKER_00] i oni koji

246
00:17:48,779 --> 00:17:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] najpozitivnije govore,

247
00:17:51,019 --> 00:17:51,579
[SPEAKER_00] kažu da je to

248
00:17:51,579 --> 00:17:53,839
[SPEAKER_00] najmanje loš oblik vladanja.

249
00:17:55,339 --> 00:17:57,559
[SPEAKER_00] I dobro je jedan mudra čovjek napisao

250
00:17:57,559 --> 00:17:59,640
