288
00:19:04,900 --> 00:19:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] osoba sad ljudi,

289
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je,

290
00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:07,339
