295
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:25,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ali oni doli 12,

296
00:19:25,720 --> 00:19:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] Bože te sačuvaj,

297
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:29,140
[SPEAKER_00] nitko ih za zeta ne bi htio.

298
00:19:29,140 --> 00:19:31,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sad šta se događa?

299
00:19:31,900 --> 00:19:33,559
