304
00:19:38,079 --> 00:19:39,640
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad ja okružim marina,

305
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,779
[SPEAKER_00] a ja okružio i ovih drugih 13.

306
00:19:42,779 --> 00:19:46,400
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je to smišljeno,

307
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:50,799
[SPEAKER_00] kako je to ta demokracija varka i laž.

308
00:19:50,799 --> 00:19:52,779
[SPEAKER_00] Laž.

309
00:19:52,779 --> 00:19:54,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo,

310
00:19:54,619 --> 00:19:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] birati nam je manje zlo.

311
00:19:56,539 --> 00:20:02,619
[SPEAKER_00] Vatikanskim koncilu Gaudium S5 kaže broj 74.

312
00:20:02,619 --> 00:20:06,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ako vlast prelazi nadležnosti

313
00:20:06,400 --> 00:20:09,400
