315
00:20:13,559 --> 00:20:15,240
[SPEAKER_00] Nužnost.

316
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:21,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ovo počinje sada zbilja tlačenje,

317
00:20:21,259 --> 00:20:25,519
