320
00:20:32,420 --> 00:20:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] nego preodgajati narod.

321
00:20:35,079 --> 00:20:38,819
[SPEAKER_00] Nas se želi preodgajati,

322
00:20:38,819 --> 00:20:41,980
