328
00:20:56,460 --> 00:20:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] i prije ih je bilo,

329
00:20:58,039 --> 00:20:59,259
[SPEAKER_00] nisu mediji javljali,

330
00:20:59,259 --> 00:21:01,480
