333
00:21:05,960 --> 00:21:09,119
[SPEAKER_00] Šta mi imamo od toga?

334
00:21:09,119 --> 00:21:12,319
[SPEAKER_00] I ona tamo priča, kaže,

335
00:21:12,319 --> 00:21:15,559
