337
00:21:22,359 --> 00:21:23,900
[SPEAKER_00] Čujete li vi šta, šta ja govorim?

338
00:21:23,900 --> 00:21:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] No, ne da nam ja da čujem,

339
00:21:25,539 --> 00:21:27,579
