342
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:38,059
[SPEAKER_00] smanjiti ubojstva u Zagrebu.

343
00:21:38,059 --> 00:21:42,359
[SPEAKER_00] Tu bi Matan iz Prosijaka i Sinova rekao,

344
00:21:42,359 --> 00:21:44,640
