355
00:22:10,539 --> 00:22:14,299
[SPEAKER_00] E to je to, preodgoj.

356
00:22:14,299 --> 00:22:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] Oni nas žele preodgajati,

357
00:22:16,519 --> 00:22:18,700
