00:29:25,019 --> 00:29:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] za koju ti krvario.

578
00:29:26,059 --> 00:29:27,420
[SPEAKER_00] To se Hrvatsko je dogodilo,

579
00:29:27,420 --> 00:29:28,259
[SPEAKER_00] zato nema blagoslova.

580
00:29:28,259 --> 00:29:30,559
[SPEAKER_00] Dok vidiš u Londonu,

581
00:29:30,559 --> 00:29:31,460
[SPEAKER_00] oni svoje,

582
00:29:31,460 --> 00:29:32,980
[SPEAKER_00] oni su biti agresori.

583
00:29:35,740 --> 00:29:37,759
[SPEAKER_00] drže do njih kao do velikana,

584
00:29:37,759 --> 00:29:39,660
[SPEAKER_00] a mi branili, krvarli,

585
00:29:39,660 --> 00:29:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] naši branitelji,

586
00:29:40,579 --> 00:29:41,839
