589
00:29:45,599 --> 00:29:48,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se ne bojim

590
00:29:48,059 --> 00:29:49,700
[SPEAKER_00] za domovinu.

591
00:29:49,700 --> 00:29:51,759
[SPEAKER_00] Dokle goti jedan od njih

592
