593
00:29:52,559 --> 00:29:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] jedan dostaje.

594
00:29:53,599 --> 00:29:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan svjedok,

595
00:29:55,380 --> 00:29:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] a imamo ih puno,

596
00:29:57,519 --> 00:29:58,119
[SPEAKER_00] Bogu hvala.

597
00:29:58,119 --> 00:29:59,759
[SPEAKER_00] Ne trebamo se brinuti.

598
00:29:59,759 --> 00:30:02,759
[SPEAKER_00] Tu nema dileme.

599
