[SPEAKER_00] samo mi se moramo hrabljiti.

600
00:30:06,140 --> 00:30:08,279
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je Hrušćov,

601
00:30:08,279 --> 00:30:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] čuli ste vi za njega,

602
00:30:09,380 --> 00:30:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] naslijedio je on Stalina.

603
00:30:11,119 --> 00:30:16,119
[SPEAKER_00] I govori on tamo u njihovoj dumi,

604
00:30:16,119 --> 00:30:18,140
[SPEAKER_00] ti je centralni komitet,

605
00:30:18,140 --> 00:30:19,660
[SPEAKER_00] Sovjet i tako dalje,

606
00:30:19,660 --> 00:30:21,400
