607
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:26,660
[SPEAKER_00] I on govori protiv Stalina.

608
00:30:26,660 --> 00:30:29,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je bilo zla,

609
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:31,799
