647
00:31:46,019 --> 00:31:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo dužni opominjati.

648
00:31:47,980 --> 00:31:49,279
[SPEAKER_00] Ezekijel prorok kaže,

649
00:31:49,279 --> 00:31:51,279
