794
00:35:53,260 --> 00:35:54,300
[SPEAKER_00] betonirale.

795
00:35:54,300 --> 00:35:55,119
[SPEAKER_00] Pa šta?

796
00:35:55,119 --> 00:35:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] I tako vam mogu brojiti

797
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] do kraja.

798
00:35:58,519 --> 00:35:59,639
[SPEAKER_00] To pa šta?

799
00:35:59,639 --> 00:36:00,300
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

800
00:36:00,300 --> 00:36:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] drugi tako čine,

801
00:36:01,619 --> 00:36:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] i ja tako čini,

802
00:36:02,500 --> 00:36:03,059
[SPEAKER_00] nema Boga,

803
00:36:03,059 --> 00:36:03,760
[SPEAKER_00] nema pravde,

804
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:04,599
[SPEAKER_00] nema suda,

805
00:36:04,599 --> 00:36:05,159
[SPEAKER_00] nema ničega.

806
00:36:05,159 --> 00:36:05,579
[SPEAKER_00] Pa šta?

807
00:36:05,579 --> 00:36:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] I druga?

808
00:36:09,500 --> 00:36:12,320
[SPEAKER_00] Znate,

809
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:12,860
[SPEAKER_00] ono dođu,

810
00:36:12,860 --> 00:36:13,239
[SPEAKER_00] ne one,

811
00:36:13,239 --> 00:36:14,519
[SPEAKER_00] dođu se ono dudon.

812
00:36:14,519 --> 00:36:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] Što vi mislite,

813
00:36:16,440 --> 00:36:17,199
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

814
00:36:17,199 --> 00:36:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] ni o pobačaju?

815
00:36:18,039 --> 00:36:20,420
[SPEAKER_00] Onda dođu,

816
00:36:20,420 --> 00:36:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] ne znaš,

817
00:36:20,880 --> 00:36:21,679
[SPEAKER_00] ono na pučle,

818
00:36:21,679 --> 00:36:22,599
[SPEAKER_00] se usne ovdje,

819
00:36:22,599 --> 00:36:23,679
[SPEAKER_00] tko voli,

820
00:36:23,679 --> 00:36:24,360
[SPEAKER_00] neki izvoli.

821
00:36:28,260 --> 00:36:28,619
[SPEAKER_00] Znate,

822
00:36:28,619 --> 00:36:29,340
[SPEAKER_00] kako mi to,

823
00:36:29,340 --> 00:36:29,940
[SPEAKER_00] jedno,

824
00:36:29,940 --> 00:36:30,760
[SPEAKER_00] svi relativiziramo,

825
00:36:30,760 --> 00:36:31,760
[SPEAKER_00] sad ja gledam neke ove,

826
00:36:31,760 --> 00:36:32,320
[SPEAKER_00] koji su čak,

827
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:32,800
[SPEAKER_00] oko na ime,

828
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:33,659
[SPEAKER_00] naši katolici,

829
00:36:33,659 --> 00:36:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] ovo kad se pita o pobačaj,

830
00:36:35,079 --> 00:36:35,719
[SPEAKER_00] pa oni počnu,

831
00:36:35,719 --> 00:36:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] znaš,

832
00:36:36,079 --> 00:36:37,019
[SPEAKER_00] od Markova,

833
00:36:37,019 --> 00:36:37,599
[SPEAKER_00] Konaka,

834
00:36:37,599 --> 00:36:38,239
[SPEAKER_00] pa ovo,

835
00:36:38,239 --> 00:36:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] nema o tome,

836
00:36:40,579 --> 00:36:42,159
[SPEAKER_00] tu nema filozofije.

837
00:36:42,159 --> 00:36:44,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi li zna,

838
00:36:44,139 --> 00:36:44,579
[SPEAKER_00] daj ne?

839
00:36:44,579 --> 00:36:45,300
[SPEAKER_00] Isu je rekao,

840
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:46,280
[SPEAKER_00] vaš odgovornik bude da,

841
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:46,559
[SPEAKER_00] da,

842
00:36:46,559 --> 00:36:47,300
[SPEAKER_00] ili ne, ne.

843
00:36:47,300 --> 00:36:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ne može kršćanska Isusova duša,

844
00:36:50,659 --> 00:36:51,840
[SPEAKER_00] koja je gospodina susrla,

845
00:36:51,840 --> 00:36:52,760
[SPEAKER_00] reći,

846
00:36:53,099 --> 00:36:54,639
[SPEAKER_00] za stvari koje su grijeh,

847
00:36:54,639 --> 00:36:55,579
[SPEAKER_00] tko voli,

848
00:36:55,579 --> 00:36:56,139
[SPEAKER_00] neki izvoli.

849
00:36:56,139 --> 00:36:59,719
[SPEAKER_00] E to nas ko šta,

850
00:36:59,719 --> 00:37:00,860
[SPEAKER_00] to je ta laž,

851
00:37:00,860 --> 00:37:01,400
[SPEAKER_00] paradoks,

852
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:02,599
[SPEAKER_00] taj pa šta,

853
00:37:02,599 --> 00:37:03,900
[SPEAKER_00] i tko voli,

854
00:37:03,900 --> 00:37:04,780
[SPEAKER_00] neki izvoli.

855
00:37:04,780 --> 00:37:08,199
[SPEAKER_00] Izvoli.

856
00:37:08,199 --> 00:37:11,239
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala lijepo.

